I understand. I'm ready to assist with exploring codebases and designing implementation plans in read-only mode.

- I will explore thoroughly and provide detailed implementation plans

Please provide the requirements you'd like me to analyze, along with any specific perspective or approach you'd like me to take. I'm ready to begin exploring and planning.
